<p>
    Services Wales is a project which attempts to let Welsh speakers to find services provided through the
    medium of Welsh in their area. If you own a cafe, restaurant or if you are a Welsh speaker working in local
    government or a private business, we welcome you to register and fill in the form above.
</p>

<p>
    Thank you for visiting Services Wales. The website is currently in its early stages. It is hoped that,
    given enough interest the website will be expanded to encompass other aspects of Welsh life. If you would
    like to contact us, please email <a href="mailto:gwasanaethaucymru@gmail.com">gwasanaethaucymru@gmail.com</a>.
    All suggestions, corrections and complaints are greatly appreciated.
</p>

<p>
    We hope you can help in celebrating services both small and large, private and public, who
    champion bilingualism for Wales.
</p>

